## Weekly Metrics

```dataview
TABLE WITHOUT ID
  file.link AS "Day",
  bp_systolic + "/" + bp_diastolic AS "BP",
  hrv AS "HRV",
  sleep_score AS "Sleep",
  energy AS "Energy",
  strain AS "Strain",
  emotional_eating AS "Emot?"
FROM "02-Cowork/Health/Daily"
WHERE date >= this.week_start AND date <= this.week_end
SORT date ASC

